{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019zzkt2zVNLLibo6YfN663e","type":"tool_result","content":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/sprint/types.ts-1-/**\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/sprint/types.ts-2- * Types for the sprint module.\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/sprint/types.ts-3- */\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/sprint/types.ts-4-\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/sprint/types.ts-5-import type { StoryStatus, ActionItem, AcVerdict } from '../../types/state.js';\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/sprint/types.ts-6-\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/sprint/types.ts-7-/** Partial update for live run progress fields */\nsrc/modules/sprint/types.ts:8:export interface RunProgressUpdate {\nsrc/modules/sprint/types.ts-9-  readonly currentStory?: string | null;\nsrc/modules/sprint/types.ts-10-  readonly currentPhase?: 'create' | 'dev' | 'review' | 'verify' | null;\nsrc/modules/sprint/types.ts-11-  readonly lastAction?: string | null;\nsrc/modules/sprint/types.ts-12-  readonly acProgress?: string | null;\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/sprint/types.ts-13-}\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/sprint/types.ts-14-\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/sprint/types.ts-15-/** A story selected for development */\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/sprint/types.ts-16-export interface StorySelection {\nsrc/modules/sprint/types.ts-17-  readonly key: string;\nsrc/modules/sprint/types.ts-18-  readonly title: string;\n--\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-97-};\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-98-```\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-99-\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-100-### Atomic Write Pattern (Already Implemented)\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-101-\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-102-`writeStateAtomic()` in `state.ts` already uses `writeFileSync` to a `.sprint-state.json.tmp` temp file, then `renameSync` to the final path. This is the standard POSIX atomic write pattern — `rename(2)` is atomic on all major filesystems. AC #4 is satisfied by the existing implementation; this story just needs to ensure all new writes go through `writeStateAtomic`.\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-103-\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-104-### RunProgressUpdate Type\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-105-\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-106-```typescript\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md:107:interface RunProgressUpdate {\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-108-  readonly currentStory?: string | null;\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-109-  readonly currentPhase?: 'create' | 'dev' | 'review' | 'verify' | null;\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-110-  readonly lastAction?: string | null;\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-111-  readonly acProgress?: string | null;\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-112-}\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-113-```\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-114-\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-115-Partial updates are important — when updating `acProgress`, you don't want to clear `currentStory` and `currentPhase`.\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-116-\n/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/0-1-sprint-state-live-updates.md-117-### harness-run.md Integration Points\n\n[Showing results with pagination = limit: 60, offset: 0]"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01VDEDGGGLstVGgA3jxfk8Nj","session_id":"6707468c-554d-4568-9ea5-0d04d4a85f59","uuid":"87a81a26-fa69-46e4-8be9-22867765e9a1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T10:17:57.422Z"}
