{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Vqf2RnmRwegjyUyCW2gegs","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01VgzRp7XsCtU87oSa5QDrmq","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"- **Pre-existing TS compilation errors (~100 lines):** Persisted across Epics 8, 9, 10. Prioritize 15-4-fix-ts-compilation-errors.","new_string":"- **Pre-existing TS compilation errors (~100 lines):** Persisted across Epics 8, 9, 10. Prioritize 15-4-fix-ts-compilation-errors.\n\n### 11-1-unified-sprintstate-schema-versioning — create-story (2026-03-24T10:19Z)\n\n- **Epic number reuse confusion:** Previous sprint had a different Epic 11 (Retrospective Integration). Current architecture-v3.md Epic 11 (Unified State) reuses the number. sprint-status.yaml is authoritative.\n- **Stub overwrite:** Existing story file was a 3-AC stub. Overwrote entirely with 19 ACs, 7 tasks.\n- **Diverged from epic definition:** Architecture says delete `.story_retries`/`.flagged_stories` during migration. Deferred to 11-3 (reconciliation) to avoid data loss risk on interrupted migration.\n- **Circular dependency risk:** retry-state.ts → getSprintState() → migrateFromOldFormat() potential cycle.\n- **Format mismatch:** `.story_retries` uses space separators but `retry-state.ts` uses `=` separators. Post-refactor this becomes irrelevant."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":245,"cache_read_input_tokens":48150,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":245},"output_tokens":72,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6707468c-554d-4568-9ea5-0d04d4a85f59","uuid":"7b8182eb-2757-4068-8d97-f948fb3d9b86"}
